title: Box
content:
Box may refer to:

  • Aluft aloft box, used in Gnome Restaurant
  • An empty box, used to create fish food
  • Bauble box, used in the 2005 Christmas event
    • Puppet box
  • Box of Health, in the Stronghold of Security
  • Box trap, used in Hunter
  • Boxing ring, built in a Combat Room
    • Boxing gloves, obtained from a weapons rack in a combat room
    • Unarmed combat, which can also be known as boxing
  • Fancy dress boxes
    • Fancy dress box space
    • Oak fancy dress box
    • Teak fancy dress box
    • Mahogany fancy dress box
  • Heavy box, obtained during Royal Trouble
    • Empty box, a useless item received from Royal Trouble
  • Herb box, obtained from Nightmare Zone
  • Imp-in-a-box, caught with Hunter
    • Magic box
  • Mystery box, a random event reward
  • Power box, obtained on the Dorgesh-Kaan Agility Course
  • Puzzle box, obtained on hard-level Treasure Trails
  • Rok's Chocs Box, a store in Nardah
  • Seed box, obtained from Tithe Farm
  • Shoe box, built in a Bedroom
  • Strange box
  • Small box hedge, a plant in a Formal Garden
  • Tall box hedge, a plant in a Formal Garden
  • Tinderbox, for lighting fires
    • Damp tinderbox
    • Golden tinderbox
  • Toy boxes
    • Mahogany toy box
    • Oak toy box
    • Teak toy box
    • Toy box space
